## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="c8565-102">Se <xref:System.ServiceModel.BasicHttpSecurity.Mode%2A> está configurado para realizar a autenticação de cliente no nível da mensagem, essa enumeração controla o tipo de credencial de cliente.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c8565-102">If <xref:System.ServiceModel.BasicHttpSecurity.Mode%2A> is configured to perform client authentication at the message level, this enumeration controls the client credential type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c8565-103">Nome de usuário e o certificado X.509 para uso devem ser provisionados por meio de um <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IEndpointBehavior> da instância que implementa o <xref:System.ServiceModel.Security.SecurityCredentialsManager> ponto de extensibilidade; em um padrão comum caso, isso é <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ClientCredentials>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c8565-103">Both username and X.509 certificate to use must be provisioned through an <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IEndpointBehavior> instance which implements the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Security.SecurityCredentialsManager> extensibility point; in a common default case this is <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ClientCredentials>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="c8565-104">A credencial do cliente no caso do certificado deve ser especificada usando o <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ClientCredentials.ClientCertificate%2A> propriedade do <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ClientCredentials> classe.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c8565-104">The client credential in the certificate case must be specified using the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ClientCredentials.ClientCertificate%2A> property of the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ClientCredentials> class.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="c8565-105">A credencial do cliente no caso de nome de usuário deve ser especificada usando o <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ClientCredentials.UserName%2A> propriedade do <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ClientCredentials> classe.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c8565-105">The client credential in the username case must be specified using the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ClientCredentials.UserName%2A> property of the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ClientCredentials> class.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="c8565-106">Além disso, quando o modo de segurança de mensagem é usado, o cliente deve ser provisionado com o certificado do serviço.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c8565-106">In addition, when message security mode is used, the client must be provisioned with the service's certificate.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c8565-107">A credencial de serviço neste caso deve ser especificada usando o <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ClientCredentials.ServiceCertificate%2A> propriedade no <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ClientCredentials> classe.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c8565-107">The service credential in this case must be specified using the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ClientCredentials.ServiceCertificate%2A> property on the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ClientCredentials> class.</span></span>  
  
   
  
